June the 18th
My dear Mrs Carpenter,
after having send you a letter I got a telegram signed by the Arts Club saying that you are away. 
Now I understand that the decision to cancel my exhibition was taken while you were away and I am hopeful that you will change
My address in Paris will be c/o Persian Legation
